## 🎭 Framework Extractions

Viktron integrates battle-tested patterns from leading agent frameworks:

| Framework | Pattern | Implementation |
|-----------|---------|----------------|
| **CrewAI** | Manager quality checks | `pm.js` → `_quality_check()` validates dev output |
| **LangGraph** | Step checkpointing | `checkpoint.js` saves state before each step |
| **AutoGen** | GroupChat planning | CEO + PM plan together before execution |
| **Magentic-One** | Task & Progress Ledger | `progress_ledger.js` with stall detection |
| **Spacebot** | Token compaction | 80%/85%/95% context threshold trimming |
| **OpenAI SDK** | History compression | `orchestrator.js` compresses handoff transcripts |
| **Google ADK** | Tiered memory | 3-tier temp/session/permanent storage |
| **Strands** | Tool library | File, shell, code, browser tools in `tools/` |
| **MCP** | JSON-RPC tool calls | `mcp_adapter.js` exposes tools via protocol |
| **LlamaIndex** | Semantic routing | Embeddings + cosine similarity for agent selection |
| **CAMEL** | Inception prompts | YAML definitions auto-prepend system messages |
| **Sem. Kernel** | Skills registry | Auto-discovers `skills/*.md` files |

